data.description: **REDUCED! PLUS Seller will pay UP TO $14,000 towards a Permanent or Temporary Rate Buy Down AND / OR Buyer Closing Cost with an acceptable offer**  Get ready to infuse your personality into this beautiful Long Pine Estates residence as you unlock the potential of this 3-bedroom, 2-bath Craftsman-style home. Picture the possibilities as you shape this space into your own.  With a touch of care, this residence can evolve into your forever home. Upon entering, the open concept layout eagerly awaits your creative input, providing the perfect canvas to design a space that truly embodies your style. The kitchen, equipped with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and stylish stained wood cabinets with 42" uppers, is well-appointed. The living room features a gas fireplace, ensuring cozy warmth on chilly evenings. Indulge in the spa-like atmosphere of your master retreat with a large whirlpool tub, separate shower, double vanity, private water closet, and a spacious walk-in closet. Not to be overlooked, the additional bedrooms are strategically placed, providing a sense of separation and individual space that offers privacy and tranquility for all residents. Step outside to the private screened-in back porch and envision creating a tranquil outdoor retreat amid the shaded backyard with mature trees, perfect for entertaining. Conveniently located just 10 minutes from downtown Fairhope, this property not only offers the potential for a dream home but also provides easy access to the lively atmosphere, shops, and attractions of the area. Moreover, it's just a short drive from Mobile, Downtown Fairhope, Pensacola, and the sandy white beaches of The Gulf. Don't miss the opportunity to make this Craftsman gem your home sweet home. Schedule a showing today and imagine the incredible home that awaits you in this wonderful subdivision. A 1-year home warranty will be provided. Home is being sold 'as-is".
